### Platform summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/platform/summary

### Platform application scorecards
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/platform/scorecards

### Search and sort platform scorecards
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/platform/scorecards?q=payroll&owner_team=platform&risk_level=low&min_score=80&sort=score&order=desc

### Platform environment drift reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/platform/environment-drift

### Filter drift reports by environment and drift level
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/platform/environment-drift?q=LOG_LEVEL&type=production&status=active&drift_level=high&max_drift_score=80&sort=score
